<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-1782] async only defined in silverlight</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-1782</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The async pattern is available in C# 5 on .NET 4.5. Thus, it shouldn&apos;t only be for Silverlight.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12623038">THRIFT-1782</key>
            <summary>async only defined in silverlight</summary>
